        |
Camera Registry and Stream Sessions
        |
Stream Capture Layer
        |
Frame Queue and Frame Processing Layer
        |
Motion Detection / Activity Gate
        |
Object Detection and Zone-Aware Filtering
        |
Human Tracking and Movement Analysis
        |
Behavior Analysis and Optional Identity Analysis
        |
Event Rules and Severity Classification
        |
Event Dispatch Layer
